text: Aboubacar Ibrahima Toungara (born 15 November 1994) is a Malian footballer. He was part of the youth team that made it to the group stage 2013 FIFA U-20 World Cup with Mali squad . ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Malian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Sportspeople from Bamako Category:Chabab Atlas Khénifra players
